    public class CorrelateurPompier
extends AbstractCorrelateur
implements PompierCorrelatorStateI
    The class CorrelateurPompier implements a component that can send and receive events, demand l'executor fire staion connected to execute actions

    The component implements the PompierCorrelatorStateI interface to verify the correlate condition,trigger demand of execution action
